---

<section id="about" class="relative py-24 bg-slate-950 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background Elements -->
  <div
    class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-slate-800 to-transparent"
  >
  </div>
  <div
    class="absolute -top-[300px] -right-[300px] w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-teal-900/5 rounded-full blur-[100px]"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-16 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-start">
      <!-- Section Title & Intro (Left Column) -->
      <div class="md:col-span-12 lg:col-span-5 sticky top-24">
        <span
          class="inline-block px-3 py-1 mb-6 text-xs tracking-widest text-teal-400 uppercase border border-teal-900/50 rounded-full bg-teal-900/10"
        >
          About Me
        </span>

        <h2
          class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-slate-100 leading-tight mb-6"
        >
          Beyond the <br />
          <span class="text-teal-500 italic font-serif">White Coat</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="text-lg text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          I view dentistry not just as a medical discipline, but as a fine blend
          of engineering and art. Every restoration, every procedure is an
          opportunity to restore not just function, but confidence.
        </p>

        <div
          class="relative w-full aspect-[4/5] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 shadow-2xl group"
        >
          <!-- Placeholder for a secondary image (e.g. working in clinic) -->
          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center bg-slate-800 text-slate-600"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-16 h-16 opacity-20"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="1"
                d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-950 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-60"
          >
          </div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 right-6">
            <p class="text-white font-medium text-lg">Dr. Muhammad</p>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Dental Surgeon</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content & Details (Right Column) -->
      <div class="md:col-span-12 lg:col-span-7 space-y-16 lg:pt-12">
        <!-- Philosophy Block -->
        <div class="group">
          <h3
            class="text-2xl font-serif text-slate-200 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3"
          >
            <span
              class="w-8 h-px bg-teal-500/50 group-hover:w-16 transition-all duration-300"
            ></span>
            My Philosophy
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-lg pt-5">
            My approach is grounded in <strong
              >minimally invasive dentistry</strong
            >â€”preserving as much natural tooth structure as possible while
            strictly adhering to biomimetic principles. I believe in
            evidence-based practice, where every decision is backed by the
            latest research and clinical success standards.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Skills Compass -->
        <div
          class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 bg-slate-900/50 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-800/50"
        >
          <!-- Skill 1: Strategic Planning -->
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div
              class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-teal-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-teal-400 mb-4"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="1.5"
                  d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-white font-medium">Strategic Planning</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
              Comprehensive treatment planning considering long-term oral
              health.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Skill 2: Clinical Precision -->
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div
              class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-indigo-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-400 mb-4"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="1.5"
                  d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.384-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-white font-medium">Clinical Precision</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
              Meticulous execution of procedures with attention to microscopic
              detail.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Skill 3: Patient Care -->
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div
              class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-rose-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-rose-400 mb-4"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="1.5"
                  d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-white font-medium">Patient Care</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
              Empathy-driven approach ensuring comfort and trust.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Skill 4: Continuous Learning -->
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div
              class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-amber-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-amber-400 mb-4"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="1.5"
                  d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-white font-medium">Continuous Learning</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
              Staying updated with the latest in digital dentistry.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Signature Block -->
        <div class="pt-8 border-t border-slate-800/50">
          <p class="text-slate-500 italic mb-4">
            "A healthy smile is the best accessory one can wear."
          </p>
          <div class="font-handwriting text-3xl text-teal-400 opacity-80">
            - Dr. Zahrawi
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
